  "detailed_description": "It’s Hero Time! <br><br>Ben, Gwen, and Grandpa Max once again have their cross-country road trip in the Rust Bucket cut short by super villains and their evil, world-threatening plans. <br>As Ben Tennyson, it’s up to you to save the world. Take on some of Ben’s most infamous enemies, including Zombozo, Queen Bee, and the Weatherheads. Unlock and transform into all ten of Ben’s incredible alien forms. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/703180/extras/7cfb0f258bf335a778dd5fa3c429ac23.poster.avif?t=1670259406\" width=650 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/703180/extras/7cfb0f258bf335a778dd5fa3c429ac23.webm?t=1670259406\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/703180/extras/7cfb0f258bf335a778dd5fa3c429ac23.mp4?t=1670259406\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Use each alien’s powerful combat moves – including Ultimate Attacks - to lay the beat-down on enemies with devastating combos, and solve puzzles with each alien’s unique abilities as you unravel exciting new stories in three all-new playable episodes. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/703180/extras/4cefaebffad46e0cfdc550e95ecdcc6d.poster.avif?t=1670259406\" width=650 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/703180/extras/4cefaebffad46e0cfdc550e95ecdcc6d.webm?t=1670259406\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/703180/extras/4cefaebffad46e0cfdc550e95ecdcc6d.mp4?t=1670259406\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Being a hero can be hard work…but it's a whole lot of fun!<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Star as Ben 10 in three exciting new episodes and unravel an exciting new story, packed with humour and action.<br></li><li>Unlock and transform into 10 incredible alien creatures with unique abilities.<br></li><li>Save the day with explosive combat and fun puzzle-solving.<br></li><li>Meet your favourite characters and explore diverse locations.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/703180/extras/a5b3533d31f9521040a39dce07477b42.poster.avif?t=1670259406\" width=650 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/703180/extras/a5b3533d31f9521040a39dce07477b42.webm?t=1670259406\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/703180/extras/a5b3533d31f9521040a39dce07477b42.mp4?t=1670259406\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "It’s Hero Time! <br><br>Ben, Gwen, and Grandpa Max once again have their cross-country road trip in the Rust Bucket cut short by super villains and their evil, world-threatening plans. <br>As Ben Tennyson, it’s up to you to save the world. Take on some of Ben’s most infamous enemies, including Zombozo, Queen Bee, and the Weatherheads. Unlock and transform into all ten of Ben’s incredible alien forms. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/703180/extras/7cfb0f258bf335a778dd5fa3c429ac23.poster.avif?t=1670259406\" width=650 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/703180/extras/7cfb0f258bf335a778dd5fa3c429ac23.webm?t=1670259406\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/703180/extras/7cfb0f258bf335a778dd5fa3c429ac23.mp4?t=1670259406\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Use each alien’s powerful combat moves – including Ultimate Attacks - to lay the beat-down on enemies with devastating combos, and solve puzzles with each alien’s unique abilities as you unravel exciting new stories in three all-new playable episodes. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/703180/extras/4cefaebffad46e0cfdc550e95ecdcc6d.poster.avif?t=1670259406\" width=650 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/703180/extras/4cefaebffad46e0cfdc550e95ecdcc6d.webm?t=1670259406\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/703180/extras/4cefaebffad46e0cfdc550e95ecdcc6d.mp4?t=1670259406\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Being a hero can be hard work…but it's a whole lot of fun!<br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Star as Ben 10 in three exciting new episodes and unravel an exciting new story, packed with humour and action.<br></li><li>Unlock and transform into 10 incredible alien creatures with unique abilities.<br></li><li>Save the day with explosive combat and fun puzzle-solving.<br></li><li>Meet your favourite characters and explore diverse locations.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/703180/extras/a5b3533d31f9521040a39dce07477b42.poster.avif?t=1670259406\" width=650 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/703180/extras/a5b3533d31f9521040a39dce07477b42.webm?t=1670259406\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/703180/extras/a5b3533d31f9521040a39dce07477b42.mp4?t=1670259406\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
